{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_63031.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":1,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime02","nameNarration":"Monk","narration":"\"Rise and shine... Rise and shine...\"","narrationBg":"bg_adv_63031.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"Ah, ah..."},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"Nnnh...zzz...zzz..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":400,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"Oh, WAAAAAAAH!!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":105101,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"No, no, no! Dolma!@We overslept, it's late!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"...Oh, she's not here..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":300,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"Ugh...couldn't you at least wake me up!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_63011.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":833300,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"Nah, I tried...you were sleeping with your@mouth wide open, like an idiot.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"[chara:105101:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]A-An idiot?!"},{"chara":[{"id":833300,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"You really need to work on that terrible@morning attitude of yours."},{"chara":[{"id":833300}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"Remember when you overslept and were late@for our lessons before?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"Ugh... I'll be more careful..."},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"It's probably the umpteenth time I've been@scolded by Dolma for my poor mornings. ","narrationBg":"bg_adv_63011.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"Lately, it feels like I'm the one dragging@Dolma along, not the other way around."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":1,"pos":1},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"narration":"No, that's not right...@It means I'm making Dolma do things@she doesn't want to."},{"chara":[{"id":833900}],"nameLeft":"Junior Nun","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"Hey, hey, let's sneak out during our practice time."},{"chara":[{"id":833300}],"nameCenter":"Dolma","textCenter":"Ehh..."},{"chara":[{"id":833900}],"nameRight":"Junior Nun","textRight":"Come on, it'll be fun!@It's boring without you, Dolma."},{"chara":[{"id":833300}],"nameCenter":"Dolma","textCenter":"Ugh...okay, but will you do me a favor too?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.3,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833300},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"(Dolma is really popular now...)"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Yes, Dolma became quite popular at the nunnery.@She was the smartest and most athletic...@and everyone looked up to her.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_63011.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narration":"She became such a special existence."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameCenter":"Teacher Monk","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Alright, everyone, please take your seats.@We're starting our lessons."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833800}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"nameLeft":"Junior Nun","textLeft":"Yes!"},{"chara":[{"id":833900}],"nameRight":"Junior Nun","textRight":"See you later."},{"chara":[{"id":833300}],"nameCenter":"Dolma","textCenter":"Take care..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833300}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":105101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"(...I've become quite the underachiever...)"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Initially, everyone had high expectations@for me as a miracle worker,","narrationBg":"bg_adv_63011.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"narration":"but when they realized I wasn't anything special,@just a boring person, they all distanced themselves."},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"(But that's okay...@No, actually...)"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"It felt comfortable not having anyone@expect anything from me.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_63011.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51191_historia_tibet/memoria_1896.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story02","nameNarration":"Teacher Monk","narration":"―Teacher Monk―@...An \"object\" is a specific existence@in and of itself.","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":10.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"―Teacher Monk―@However, it can undergo infinite transformations@depending on the viewer's perspective."},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"―Heruka―@..."},{"nameNarration":"Teacher Monk","narration":"―Teacher Monk―@Through this process, a unique relationship is born between the@object, its form, and us, mediated by desires and hopes."},{"narration":"―Teacher Monk―@It's quite fascinating, isn't it?"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"―Heruka―@Heh heh..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Well, I didn't really understand@any of that back then.","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"I didn't study at all, and the most I did was take care@of the flowers as instructed by the Lama."},{"narration":"I just couldn't keep up with all that."},{"narration":"But I didn't want to seem like I didn't understand,@so I pretended like I knew."},{"narration":"...Well, the teachers probably saw through it."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Teacher Monk","narration":"―Teacher Monk―@Now, for this question... Dolma.","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":35.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0},{"nameNarration":"Dolma","narration":"―Dolma―@Yes!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Dolma effortlessly answered the questions@given by the teacher.","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"Everyone watched her with awe and admiration."},{"narration":"Haha, it's incredible how amazing Dolma is!"},{"narration":" I couldn't help but be proud of her...@My childhood friend was amazing."},{"narration":"So..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51191_historia_tibet/memoria_1896.jpg","visible":"hide"}],"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Teacher Monk","narration":"―Teacher Monk―@Excellent...@Keep up the good work and become a Rakshasi,","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":10.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0},{"bgm":"stop","narration":"―Teacher Monk―@so you can exterminate that wicked Mongolian Army."},{"nameNarration":"Dolma","narration":"―Dolma―@Yes, I will!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Please, don't let yourself be consumed by hatred.","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"I certainly envied you for having such feelings,"},{"narration":"but I don't think they suit you."},{"narration":"To me...you're still that adorable Dolma who@used to hide behind me when we were kids..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_63041.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833900,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"id":833900}],"nameRight":"Junior Nun","textRight":"[flashEffect:flashWhite1]Hey!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Teacher Monk","textLeft":"What's with that timid stance?@Thrust the spear with force!"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Teacher Monk","textLeft":"This scarecrow is not a target―@It represents a Mongolian soldier."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Teacher Monk","textLeft":"Thrust with hatred, as if you intend to kill!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":833900,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Junior Nun","textBg":"shout","textRight":"[flashEffect:flashWhite2]...Hyaaaa!"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"After our study sessions, we had a training period where@we learned to handle spears and bows.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_63041.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"This suggests that the nunnery considers the Rakshasi@to be excellent warriors."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"narration":"...Though it seemed like the Lama opposed such thinking,@the teachers who actually provided guidance didn't@share his sentiment."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Teacher Monk","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"Next is Heruka."},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"...Yes."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":105101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833800}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Junior Nun","textLeft":"Phew... Heruka is up next, huh?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","pos":2}],"nameRight":"Junior Nun","textRight":"Hehe, even though she can't do it."},{"chara":[{"id":833900}],"nameLeft":"Junior Nun","textLeft":"I used to have high hopes for her."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Dolma","textLeft":"...No chatting during training, okay?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","pos":2}],"nameRight":"Junior Nun","textRight":"Oh, yeah... Sorry."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Junior Nun","textRight":"Go for it, Heruka~@Beat those Mongolian soldiers!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833300},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameLeft":"Teacher Monk","textLeft":"Why are you hesitating?@You won't become a Rakshasi like that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Heruka","textRight":"...Hah..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833800,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Teacher Monk","textLeft":"Wh... What's with that lack of enthusiasm...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"Teacher, can I go next?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833800,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Teacher Monk","textLeft":"...Sigh... Alright, go ahead."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833800},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":100,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"...Ehehe..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":105101}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Junior Nun","textLeft":"Well, it looks like Heruka is hopeless."},{"chara":[{"id":833900}],"nameRight":"Junior Nun","textRight":"Yep, she's definitely falling behind.@It's a relief that there are fewer competitors now."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp3.json","id":105101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"..."},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Everyone wants to become a Rakshasi,@chosen by Lord Jataka as a special existence...@I want to be that kind of special existence too.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_63041.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"The reason is simple...@I want the power to avenge my family and loved ones@who were taken by the Mongolian Army."},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"...I don't really...understand it well, though..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}